258	// Currently, there can be three forms of ZSlice:
259	// rawbuf - usual non-shm buffer
260	// shminfo - small SHM info that can be used to mount SHM buffer and get access to it's contents
261	// shmbuf - mounted SHM buffer
262	// On RX and TX we need to do the following conversion:
263	trait MapShm {
